{"title":"致拉丁美洲","authors":["晏明"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致拉丁美洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晏明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，古巴，古巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的海岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辽阔的蔗田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠绿的咖啡园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玫瑰盛开的山巅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么富庶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，古巴，古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海的明珠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雀在林子里歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩旗在大路上飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油在地下喷涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄铜在矿山闪亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么欢畅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，古巴，古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的田野撒满阳光……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你好，你好呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟草厂的工人兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你扶起倒闭的工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让新的日子在你手里生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你好，你好呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤脚的农民兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着第一次丰收的喜悦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着载满甘蔗的牛车。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你好，你好呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起义军的兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴着卷边草帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫着海岸的岗哨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何塞·马蒂的巨像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗立在哈瓦那广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呵，像挺拔的棕榈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在暴风雨的大地成长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我投入你的战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行进！行进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队一队的士兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起胸膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽着臂膀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘起！飘起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火般的大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎风招展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢声四起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪发光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾激荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我投入你的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你一同呼吸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我进入你的阵地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用诗的子弹——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向华盛顿强盗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射击！射击！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明的彩虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在古巴高高挂起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把独裁者扔进海里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撕碎海盗们的黑旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人和你肩并肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人和你在一起！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}